[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/lebensohl"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner's bid at the 2-level is a sign-off, the equivalent of the old "drop-dead" response.

So even with your great support and maximum hand, you pass.}

